				<p>Like other exchanges, it offers trades between tokens by functioning as an Automated Market Maker (AMM).</p>
				<p>What makes DefiPlaza special is that it is highly optimised to offer the lowest possible trade cost to the end user. Gas costs per trade are the lowest in the industry, and the transaction fees are very competitive at 0.1% of value traded.</p>
				<button class="btn-primary rounded-full inline-flex items-center">
				Read more
				{% include "partials/arrow-right.njk" %}
				</button>
			</div>

			<ul class="h-min flex bg-primary md:bg-primary/80 text-white md:rounded-lg md:mt-32 md:ml-8 py-4 px-4 md:px-8 space-x-8 text-center">
				<li>
					<p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold whitespace-nowrap">
						$5.34<span class="text-base font-light align-middle">m</span>
					</p>
					<h3 class="text-sm">Liquidity</h3>
				</li>
				<li>
					<p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold whitespace-nowrap">120</p>
					<h3 class="text-sm">Trading pairs</h3>
				</li>
				<li>
					<p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold whitespace-nowrap">0.1<span class="text-base font-light align-middle">%</span></p>
