			<img src="/assets/images/home/pillar.png" srcset="/assets/images/home/pillar@2x.png 2x, /assets/images/home/pillar@3x.png 3x" class="w-100">
			<div class="mx-auto md:ml-32">
				<h3 class="text-2xl">Are you feeling lost?</h3>
				<p class="mt-2">Make sure to check out our support section.</p>
